78
00:08:02,640 --> 00:08:03,320
The more scandalous, the better.

79
00:08:03,320 --> 00:08:04,270
Don't you get that?

80
00:08:04,270 --> 00:08:05,330
Mr. Cui,

81
00:08:05,520 --> 00:08:07,720
