133
00:10:09,660 --> 00:10:13,400
You're just an ordinary intern.

134
00:10:13,700 --> 00:10:16,100
Don't dream of punching above your weight.

135
00:10:17,150 --> 00:10:18,140
Miss Song,

136
00:10:18,170 --> 00:10:21,090
