146
00:10:38,860 --> 00:10:40,200
with nothing.

147
00:10:40,860 --> 00:10:43,390
I'd lose everything if I were to listen to you.

148
00:10:43,440 --> 00:10:45,570
Be careful, or I'll report you online!

149
00:10:56,160 --> 00:10:57,720
